review.reviewBody:
I made it and love it. I did a couple of minor substitutions to deal with dietary restrictions and preferences: 
1) instead of raw sugar I used Sucanat (dehydrated sugar cane juice);
2) instead of whole milk I used Almond beverage;
3) I grind my own cinnamon using cinnamon sticks to avoid possible additive fillers often found in store bought ground cinnamon;
4) did not add peaches.
